{"lastModified":1773749581293,"uri":"c::35182310185::vessel::17ffe080-ba3a-11f0-9548-87d5452668cc","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"The Wally Vantanera is a legendary yacht that combines cutting-edge design with effortless comfort, making her the ultimate choice for an unforgettable charter. At just over 30 metres, her sleek carbon-fibre hull, designed by German Frers and brought to life by Luca Bassani’s Wally Yachts, delivers both exhilarating performance under sail and refined elegance at rest.\n\nOriginally launched in 2003 and refitted in both 2008 and 2025, Vantanera has been meticulously maintained and continuously upgraded by her professional crew. With a Southern Spars mast and boom, ECsix carbon rigging, full sets of North Sails for racing and cruising, and the latest navigation and electronics, she’s as thrilling for keen sailors  as she is comfortable for those who prefer to relax on deck.","blueprint":{"name":"VANTANERA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::17ffe080-ba3a-11f0-9548-87d5452668cc::assets::0b580f90-ba3c-11f0-94a0-85f229bd049e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::17ffe080-ba3a-11f0-9548-87d5452668cc::assets::0b60e930-ba3c-11f0-94a0-85f229bd049e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::17ffe080-ba3a-11f0-9548-87d5452668cc::assets::0b56b000-ba3c-11f0-94a0-85f229bd049e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::17ffe080-ba3a-11f0-9548-87d5452668cc::assets::0b5f89a0-ba3c-11f0-94a0-85f229bd049e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::17ffe080-ba3a-11f0-9548-87d5452668cc::assets::0bdf40f0-ba3c-11f0-94a0-85f229bd049e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::17ffe080-ba3a-11f0-9548-87d5452668cc::assets::0b559e90-ba3c-11f0-94a0-85f229bd049e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::17ffe080-ba3a-11f0-9548-87d5452668cc::assets::0b5836a0-ba3c-11f0-94a0-85f229bd049e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::17ffe080-ba3a-11f0-9548-87d5452668cc::assets::e7d295e0-ba3b-11f0-94a0-85f229bd0